column3: “Such a delight to smoke this strain is very soothing and relaxing. Perfect for lazy evenings at the house or as a nightcap. Has a sweet berry hint wrapped with a earthy piney blast and a  doughy taste after exhaling.”

“absolutely amazing, very tasty. 
and a very nice mellow high.”
“Smooth strain that is perfect for after work relaxation”

“This weed gave me both a head and body high at two different times, massively recommend. Made me happy and is very
 smooth to smoke. High lasts a while.”
